         </div>
         <div
            class="block basis-0 flex-shrink flex-grow p-2 md:flex-none md:w-4/5 mx-auto lg:mx-0 text-center lg:w-1/3 xl:w-5/12 lg:text-left">
            <h2
               class="text-ic-primary text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 after:w-10 after:h-1 after:mx-auto lg:after:ml-0 after:mt-4 after:bg-freshmarket-primary after:block after:rounded">
               Tu inversión paga el alquiler
            </h2>
